n active runway allows planes to fly in and taxi directly to the museumto ensure conservation of these artifacts the design followed careful environmental parameters related to temperature humidity light air pollution insects pests vibration and noisesize sq ft   sq mservicesarchitectureinterior designlandscape architecturemechanicalelectricalplumbing   engineeringawardsaia northern virginia – award of excellencefairfax county exceptional design awards program – honor awardnaiop northern virginia – award of excellence best buildingrelated relatedpeoplehok ceo president and dc design principal bill hellmuth shares his vision for the futuremapexplore the nasm udvarhazy center on google maps share this page national air and space museum  skip to content see all topics topics science  engineering african americans aircraft apollo program art astronauts astronomers astronomy aviators awards balloons  airships business all topics top stories aviation space exploration donate now favoritesfavorites search google appliance sitewide search form search entire website by keyword leave this field blank national air and space museum visit more visit one museum two locations visit us in washington dc and chantilly va to explore hundreds of the world’s most significant objects in aviation and space history  museum in dc udvarhazy center in va imax and planetarium events educators families group reservations exhibitions more exhibitions boeing milestones of flight hall learn how aviation and spaceflight transformed the world  now on view upcoming past online collections more collections lunar module lm the lunar module represents one of humanity’s greatest achievements landing people on another heavenly body search the collections about the collection objects on display archival collection preservation  restoration learn more learn stem in  don’t miss our fastpaced webcasts designed to engage students in science technology engineering and math in  minutes   multimedia gallery educa