rlooking washington dulles international airport and enough special events to keep you coming back for more including dont miss the annual air  scare and various family days throughout the year the steven f udvarhazy center can be reached by car parking fee  and is also accessible by public transportation from the washington dc area via metro and fairfax connector bus map view nearby attraction details metro general admission fee free museum admission  parking fee until pm daily operating hours regular hours  am to  pm open every day except christmas day gift shopshopping on site restrooms onsite parking charge for parking motorcoachbus parking dining information food served onsite food court accessibility handicap accessible hearing services available metro information distance to nearest metro station mileage  nearest metro station wiehle reston east metro lines silver additional metro info bus service is available from the wiehlereston east metro station via fairfax connectors  bus visit fairfaxconnectorcom for schedules and fare information udvarhazy center summer concert series city of fairfax band national air and space museum steven f udvarhazy center july   map it more hollywood goes to war wwi on the big screen the millionaires unit us naval aviators in the first world war national air and space museum steven f udvarhazy center august   map it more udvarhazy center summer concert series loudoun community band national air and space museum steven f udvarhazy center august   map it more hollywood goes to war wwi on the big screen gallipoli national air and space museum steven f udvarhazy center september   map it more hollywood goes to war wwi on the big screen the blue max national air and space museum steven f udvarhazy center october   map it more hollywood goes to war wwi on the big screen the lost squadron national air and space museum steven f udvarhazy center november   map it more free parking after pm valid starting october   more  pender drive suite